          },
          "plain_text": "We reach Macombe, and there’s only a maze of sandy roads with the odd house to be seen. We bump into someone who calls someone else. He points us in the direction, saying just keep right, and then turn right. We take a few rights and then are faced with a fork with initiation telling me to turn left, we turn right and sure enough: we arrive. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
